ILAccountingLib::load
└── it should return a storage pointer at IL_ACCOUNTING_SLOT.

ILAccountingLib::snapshot
├── when entrySqrtPriceX96 is zero
│   └── it should store zero (no revert — caller is responsible for validation).
└── when entrySqrtPriceX96 is nonzero
    ├── given the position has no existing snapshot
    │   ├── it should store entrySqrtPriceX96 at snapshots[id][positionKey].
    │   └── it should make hasSnapshot return true.
    └── given the position already has a snapshot
        └── it should overwrite the existing entrySqrtPriceX96.

ILAccountingLib::getSnapshot
├── given the position has a snapshot
│   └── it should return the stored entrySqrtPriceX96.
└── given the position has no snapshot
    └── it should return zero.

ILAccountingLib::clear
├── given the position has a snapshot
│   ├── it should set snapshots[id][positionKey] to zero.
│   └── it should make hasSnapshot return false.
└── given the position has no snapshot
    └── it should not revert (delete on zero is a no-op).

ILAccountingLib::hasSnapshot
├── given the position has a nonzero entrySqrtPriceX96
│   └── it should return true.
└── given the position has zero entrySqrtPriceX96
    └── it should return false.
